Phn 1 - Gii thiu

  • Tn ti : Weather forecast based on daily weather observations from multiple Australian weather stations .
  • Tng quan : D bo thi tit c mt vai tr to ln trong i sng kinh t, x hi. D bo ng s gip con ngi a ra nhng quyt nh ng n.
  • Mc tiu : D bo thi tit ngy tip theo c . Bin kt qu (Y) : RainTomorrow
  • Ngun : B d liu ngun n t Cc Kh tng Khi thnh vng chung c. Cc cho php s dng d liu vi Cc Kh tng c tha nhn l ngun ca d liu, theo email t Cathy Toby (C.Toby@bom.gov.au) thuc Dch v Thng tin Kh hu ca Trung tm CLimate Quc gia, 17 Thng 12 nm 2008.
  • Link ngun : https://www.rdocumentation.org/packages/rattle/versions/5.4.0/topics/weatherAUS

ngha cc bin :

  • Date: Ngy quan st (mt i tng Date).
  • Location: Tn thng thng ca v tr ca trm thi tit.
  • MinTemp: Nhit ti thiu tnh bng C.
  • MaxTemp: Nhit ti a tnh bng C.
  • Rainfall: Lng ma c ghi li trong ngy tnh bng mm.
  • Evaporation : Ci gi l bc hi ca cho loi A (mm) trong 24 gi n 9 gi sng.
  • Sunshine : S gi nng sng trong ngy.
  • WindGustDir : Hng gi git mnh nht trong 24 gi n na m.
  • WindGustSpeed : Tc (km / h) ca gi git mnh nht trong 24 gi n na m.
  • Temp9am : Nhit ( C) lc 9 gi sng.
  • RelHumid9am : m tng i (phn trm) lc 9 gi sng.
  • Cloud9am : Mt phn bu tri b my che khut lc 9 gi sng. iu ny c o bng oktas, l mt n v ca eigth. N ghi li bao nhiu vng tri b my che khut. S o 0 cho bit bu tri hon ton trong khi s 8 cho bit tri hon ton u m.
  • WindSpeed9am : Tc gi (km / gi) trung bnh trong 10 pht trc 9 gi sng.
  • Pressure9am : p sut kh quyn (hpa) gim xung mc trung bnh ca mc nc bin lc 9 gi sng.
  • Temp3pm : Nhit ( C) lc 3 gi chiu.
  • RelHumid3pm : m tng i (phn trm) lc 3 gi chiu.
  • Cloud3pm : Mt phn bu tri b my che khut (trong oktas: phn tm) lc 3 gi chiu. Xem Cload9am bit m t v cc gi tr.
  • WindSpeed3pm : Tc gi (km / gi) trung bnh trong 10 pht trc 3 gi chiu.
  • Pressure3pm : p sut kh quyn (hpa) gim xung mc trung bnh ca mc nc bin lc 3 gi chiu.
  • ChangeTemp : Thay i nhit .
  • ChangeTempDir : Hng thay i ca nhit .
  • ChangeTempMag : ln ca s thay i ca nhit .
  • ChangeWindDirect : Hng gi thay i.
  • MaxWindPeriod : Thi k gi cc i.
  • RainToday : S nguyn: 1 nu lng ma (mm) trong 24 gi n 9 gi sng vt qu 1 mm, nu khng th 0.
  • TempRange : S khc bit gia nhit ti thiu v ti a ( C) trong 24 gi n 9 gi sng.
  • PressureChange : Thay i p sut.
  • RISK_MM : Lng ma. Mt loi thc o ri ro.
  • RainTomorrow : Bin mc tiu. Ngy mai tri c ma khng?

Vit cc hm nh gi m hnh

Confussion Matrix

conm <- function(predicted,accuraty)
{
  return(table(predicted,accuraty))
}

Cc o : accuraty , recal , precision , F_measure

accuraty <-function(cm){
  return(sum(diag(cm))/sum(cm))
}
recal <- function(cm){
  return(cm[2,2]/ (cm[2,2] +cm[1,2]))
}
precision <- function(cm){
  return(cm[2,2] / (cm[2,2] +cm[2,1]))
}
F_measure <- function(recal1,precision1){
  return(2*recal1*precision1 / (recal1+precision1))
}

Mt s nhn xt vi thut ton svm :

  • Thut ton svm c phc tp kh cao , chnh xc c th c nng ln khi tng cost nhng cng ng ngha vi vic mt nhiu thi gian v ti nguyn tnh ton hn.
  • Vi nhiu dng d liu khc nhau th s c kernel (hm bin i i s) ph hp vi loi d liu hn. c 4 dng chnh vi thut ton SVM trong th vin e1071 : Linear , Polinomial , Sigmoid, Ratio basis function.
  • Thc nghim trn tp d liu cho thy kernel Ratio basis function cho chnh xc cao nht v F1-score th nh. Kernel Linear c F1-score ln nht nn c chn.
  • Ti u : vi kernel Linear khng c tham s nn cch ti u l tng cost ti mc ph hp , khng tng qu cao v s b overfiting trn tp train v kt qu khng cao trn tp test. Khi tham s cost tng ln th model s c gng fix cc im nhiu , v th Margin s gim.
  • m hnh c Generalization hn th cost phi nh , khi m hnh s t c Margin ln.
  • Tm li vi cost nh th Margin ln , khi qut cao. vi cost tng cao th chnh xc tng ln , Margin gim , chi ph tng v tc chm hn.

Phn 4 : Kt lun

  • SVM c phc tp cao , tc chm , nhy cm vi nhiu.
  • Decission tree tc chm , chnh xc cha cao.
  • Logistic Regression tc nhanh , chnh xc cha cao.
  • Random Forest tc nhanh , chnh xc cao nht nn l la chn pht trin .

Hng pht trin ti

  • Ci thin phn tin x l d liu
  • Tinh chnh cc tham s cho cc m hnh d on c tt hn
  • Tm hiu m hnh RNN(LSTM) x l d liu chui thi gian.
